00 UTC Meeting agenda Weekly updates Looking [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"kafleg\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1847:\"<p id=\"block-a384c334-61e8-42f9-9fe8-9b33e91e3db0\">The themes team conducts a meeting on the <strong>second</strong> and <strong>fourth</strong> Tuesday of the month.</p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"block-f6c3d0aa-da6d-4a76-9e50-d3535d7e2cf7\">Along with the fixed agendas, we have an open floor at the end where you can ask or share anything related to themes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"block-5442b1bd-01b0-47f2-b4e5-24038320a7f0\">We encourage all members and anyone interested to attend.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Channel: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://wordpress.slack.com/messages/themereview/\" target=\"_blank\">#themereview</a> | Time: <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20210126T1500\" target=\"_blank\">Tuesday, January 26 2021, 15:00 UTC</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Meeting agenda</h2>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Weekly updates</li><li>Looking for a volunteer to update the <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Theme_Unit_Test\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">theme unit test</a></li><li>Open Floor</li></ol><h3>Weekly Updates</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Current statistics can be found on: <a href=\"https://themes.trac.wordpress.org/\">https://themes.trac.wordpress.org/</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Themes Trac ticket graph: <a href=\"https://themes.trac.wordpress.org/ticketgraph\">https://themes.trac.wordpress.org/ticketgraph</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Open Floor</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We will discuss everything related to themes. Attendees can ask or share themes related things.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Please comment in the comment box below if you have anything to bring up during the open floor.</p>\n<p class=\"o2-appended-tags\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/themes/tags/meeting/\" class=\"tag\"><span class=\"tag-prefix\">#</span>meeting</a>, <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/themes/tags/themes-team/\" class=\"tag\"><span class=\"tag-prefix\">#</span>themes-team</a></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:97:\"https://make.wordpress.org/themes/2021/01/25/themes-team-meeting-agenda-for-january-26-2021/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"20041\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"Gutenberg + Themes: Week of Jan 18, 2021\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://make.wordpress.org/themes/2021/01/22/gutenberg-themes-week-of-jan-18-2021/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://make.wordpress.org/themes/2021/01/22/gutenberg-themes-week-of-jan-18-2021/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 22 Jan 2021 19:37:39 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Uncategorized\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"gutenberg-themes-roundup\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"https://make.wordpress.org/themes/?p=20035\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:365:\"Hello! This is the 35th weekly roundup of theme-related discussions, fixes, and developments in Gutenberg. Please weigh in on the tickets below — your voice and feedback are welcome!  Issues / Discussions: Improve editor UI on dark backgrounds. 28200 Blocks: Refactor Gallery Block as a wrapper around Image Blocks. 25940 Blocks: Add support for border [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Kjell Reigstad\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3969:\"<p>Hello! This is the 35th weekly roundup of theme-related discussions, fixes, and developments in Gutenberg.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Please weigh in on the tickets below — your voice and feedback are welcome! </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Issues / Discussions:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Improve editor UI on dark backgrounds. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/issues/28200\">28200</a></li><li>Blocks: Refactor Gallery Block as a wrapper around Image Blocks. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/pull/25940\">25940</a></li><li>Blocks: Add support for border configuration via theme.json. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/pull/28049\">28049</a></li><li>Global Styles: Discuss the default scope of each block’s style properties: <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/issues/27512\">27512</a></li><li>FSE: Improve loading methods for block styles. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/pull/28358\">28358</a></li><li>FSE: Updates to theme.json. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/issues/28163\">28163</a> / <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/pull/28110\">28110</a></li><li>FSE: Try implementing a multi-theme system. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/pull/28131\">28131</a></li><li>FSE: Themes located in a subdirectory do not load template parts. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/issues/28022\">28022</a></li><li>FSE Blocks: Add Archive Title Block. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/pull/27989\">27989</a></li><li>FSE Blocks: Navigation block: Hide more than N items. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/issues/27131\">27131</a></li></ul><p>Merged/fixed:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Blocks: Fix shifting image in Cover block. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/pull/28404\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/pull/28404\">28404</a></li><li>FSE: Parse the template before <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> gets rendered. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/pull/28319\">28319</a></li></ul><p>Overview Issues:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Full Site Editing Milestones. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/issues/24551\">24551</a></li><li>Template Tags in Full Site Editing. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/issues/22724\">22724</a> </li><li>Missing query block functionality. <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/issues/24934\">24934</a></li><li>Query and Loop block tracking: <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/issues/24762\">24762</a></li></ul><p>General Resources:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/labels/%5BFeature%5D%20Full%20Site%20Editing\">GitHub Issues: Full Site Editing</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/labels/%5BFeature%5D%20Themes\">GitHub  Issues: Themes</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/blob/master/docs/designers-developers/developers/themes/block-based-themes.md\">Block-based Themes Reference</a></li><li><a href=\"https://developer.wordpress.org/block-editor/tutorials/block-based-themes/\">Block-based Themes Tutorial</a></li><li><a href=\"https://developer.wordpress.org/block-editor/developers/themes/theme-json/\">Experimental-Themes.json</a></li><li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/themes/2020/07/05/using-the-block-editor-for-theme-parts/\">Using the Block Editor for Theme Parts</a></li><li><a href=\"https://wp.me/p29gdg-4MC\">Printing navigation-block HTML from a legacy menu in themes</a></li></ul><p>Thanks to <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jffng/\" class=\"mention\"><span class=\"mentions-prefix\">@</span>jffng</a> and <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/scruffian/\" class=\"mention\"><span class=\"mentions-prefix\">@</span>scruffian</a> for help pulling this week’s post together. Please let us know if it was helpful in the comments!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/themes/tags/gutenberg-themes-roundup/\" class=\"tag\"><span class=\"tag-prefix\">#</span>gutenberg-themes-roundup</a></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0